Features:

- day/night modus
- 1 light as indicator or 1 dark light as inidactor (n-1 burn)
- use MCP23S17 and MCP23017 in parallel for far more than 128 LEDs

- 12 LEDs for constant hours (on/off switchable)
- 60 RGB LEDs for hours/mins/secs
- lights for seconds on/off switchable
- Color for hours/mins/secs selectable
- Brightness configurable via PWM (use 1 transistor as switch)
- Brightness depending on day light (using photocell;
  http://www.amazon.de/abh%C3%A4ngig-Widerstand-Fotowiderstand-Dependent-GL5528/dp/B009AO35Q8/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1428844199&sr=8-1&keywords=photozelle )


